<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mega City Tour</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/marsalam/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Mega City Tour</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Excursia de dupamiaza catre portul orasului El Quseir pentru shopping. O oportunitate sa vezi viata de zi cu zi a oamenilor din localitate.
        In apropiere este un vechi port din perioada otomana, disponibil de vizitat. In program este vizita la Templul Coptic si veți savura un  ceai sau o cafea.
        Cina cu mancare marina va fi servita in cel mai bun restaurant cu  vedere la mare.
        <br><br>
        Adult: 45 €<br>
        Copil: 22 €<br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        luni
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        Afternoon excursion to port town of El Quseir for shopping. An opportunity to see a daily life of local people. 
        Nearby there is an old port from Ottoman peroid, available for visits. Also in the program there is a visit of Coptic 
        Temple and time for rest with tea or coffee. On the way. Will be sea food dinner in best restaurant with amazing 
        sea view,         
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        Monday
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>